<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">I modi indefiniti</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        74
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      I <strong>modi indefiniti</strong> non danno informazioni precise sulla persona che compie l'azione. Sono modi indefiniti:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>l'<strong>infinito</strong> → tentare</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>il <strong>participio</strong> → avvisato, salvato</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>il <strong>gerundio</strong> → mangiando.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold">
      I modi indefiniti hanno due tempi: il <strong>presente</strong> e il <strong>passato</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Table with verb forms -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-purple-200">
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-400 px-4 py-3 font-bold" colspan="2">INFINITO</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-400 px-4 py-3 font-bold" colspan="2">PARTICIPIO</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-400 px-4 py-3 font-bold" colspan="2">GERUNDIO</th>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-purple-100">
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Presente</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Passato</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Presente</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Passato</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Presente</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-purple-300 px-4 py-2">Passato</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">cantare</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avere cantato</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">cantante</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">cantato</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">cantando</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avendo cantato</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-purple-50">
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">premere</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avere premuto</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">premente</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">premuto</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">premendo</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avendo premuto</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">ubbidire</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avere ubbidito</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">ubbidiente</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">ubbidito</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">ubbidendo</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3">avendo ubbidito</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Explanation boxes -->
  <div class="mb-6 space-y-4">
    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-lg p-4 md:p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3">L'INFINITO</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
        Indica la forma base del verbo, quella che devi cercare nel dizionario. Preceduto da <strong>non</strong>, forma l'imperativo negativo (<em>Non parlare più!</em>) e può essere usato come nome (<em>Tra il dire e il fare c'è di mezzo il mare</em>).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-lg p-4 md:p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">IL PARTICIPIO</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
        Può essere usato come <strong>nome</strong> (<em>insegnante</em>) o come <strong>aggettivo</strong> (<em>divertente</em>). Al passato è usato per formare i tempi composti del verbo con l'ausiliare essere o avere (<em>È uscito di casa e ha dimenticato le chiavi</em>).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl border-4 border-orange-200 shadow-lg p-4 md:p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-orange-700 mb-3">IL GERUNDIO</h3>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
        Indica un'azione che avviene in stretta relazione con un'altra (<em>Sbagliando si impara!</em>).
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi pp. 168-169</p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
